If the same report is generated **more than three times in 30 days**, prompt the user to schedule or pipeline it.

## Maximum File Length: 300 Lines

When a file exceeds this size, propose a refactor and split responsibility.

## Unit Tests First for Core Finance/Billing Logic

Tests must cover **happy path and one failure path** at minimum for any new function touching core finance or billing logic.

## Mock Data Only Inside Test Suites

**Never introduce stubs or fake data** in development or production code.

## Default Measurement System: Metric

Distances, weights, and volumes must use **SI units**.

## Link to Existing KPIs

When a placeholder KPI already exists in dashboards, **link to it instead of rebuilding** the visualization.

## Customer Data Protection

Cursor must **prompt before storing any non-public customer data** outside approved databases.

## Semantic Versioning

Use **semver-compliant version bumps** in `package__init__.py` whenever a public interface changes.

## Function Documentation

**Always include an inline docstring** explaining purpose, inputs, outputs, and side effects for every new function.

